You are given a JSON array of calendar events for 2024-05-19. Each event has fields 'title', 'start_time', 'end_time' in format 'YYYY-MM-DD HH:MM'. Determine whether the time slot from 2024-05-19 12:00 to 2024-05-19 13:00 is free (i.e., no event overlaps any part of this interval). Return a JSON object with a single boolean field 'free' indicating if the slot is free. Use the variable [
  {
    "title": "Project Kick-off",
    "start_time": "2024-05-19 10:00",
    "end_time": "2024-05-19 11:00"
  },
  {
    "title": "One-on-One with Manager",
    "start_time": "2024-05-19 11:00",
    "end_time": "2024-05-19 11:30"
  }
] as the events array.
